        "href": "https://hummingbot.io/blog/2020-07-deploying-hummingbot-on-a-raspberry-pi/"
      }}>{`Deploying Hummingbot on a Raspberry Pi`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`The only way to currently install Hummingbot on a Raspberry Pi is by downloading the source files from GitHub and compiling and running from source. This adds a few more steps than downloading binaries or running from Docker, but below we have provided a step-by-step guide to walk you through the process.`}</p>
